    {
      "chinese": "[---]\r\n早期，祭師分為祭師與遞承者兩個階層。遞承者有三類：芽生、靈童與學徒。其中芽生與靈童因年紀過小，僅見習和參與觀察，並未接受完整的訓練與工作分配。祭師則有傳承者、博哲者，及紅衣者三級。傳承者為傳授者，博哲者為專業者，已接近祖靈而隨心所欲的紅衣者乃為思想者及創新者。",
      "ab": "naayaw malatusa ku mapalaway, izaw ku mapalaway, atu patududay a katatungdud, tulu ku nu patududay, u salangawan, mutingdahang atu minanamay. labu u salangawan atu mutingdahang tada adidi’ tatu ku mihecaan, kyu pilihiza a dada’ miazih, caay pitanam miecaw atu mawawada’ tu kawaw. mapalaway izaw ku masaydan, kusuday, atu silingan tulu a katatungdud, masaydan u pasubana’ay, kusuday u samatinengay tu kawaw, micapi tu kakawsan kilul sananay tu nabalucu’an ku silingan, u misabalucu’ay atu misabaluhay. ",
